The application provides a basic implementation of CRUD services for Product and Order management

Prerequisites:
 - Apache Maven 3.6.3 or later needs to be installed on the local machine
 - The latest version of Docker Desktop needs to be installed on the local machine

How to install and run:
 1. from cmd(windows)/terminal(unix based os), cd to the root of the project and run a maven build with the following command:
    mvn clean package -DskipTests
 2. from cmd(windows)/terminal(unix based os), cd to the root of the project and run docker compose by the following command:
    docker-compose up
 3. Once the docker images are downloaded and/or created and the containers are running, the application is ready to be used
 4. In order to use the application see the swagger api doc of the project